
## New Chat Document Upload Fix

### Problem:
- Documents uploaded to new chats had NULL session_id
- Chat sessions only created when first message is sent
- RAG couldn't find documents without session association

### Solution Implemented:
1. **Backend**: Added /documents/update-session endpoint
   - Updates document session associations after chat starts
   - Handles UUID format normalization
   - Creates chat session if needed

2. **Frontend**: Modified sendMessage to update document sessions
   - When sending a message with attachments
   - Calls update-session API to link documents to chat
   - Documents get properly associated even if uploaded before chat starts

3. **Flow**:
   - User uploads document (no session yet)
   - User sends first message with question
   - System creates chat session
   - System updates document to link to new session
   - RAG can now find and use the document

### Result:
Users can now upload documents to new chats and ask questions immediately\!

